{
  "stem": "3928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or for instance, one time, one of the underground men, whom I gave a German uniform, at the time, because certain places I could not go alone, naturally.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he wasn't never in a camp, because I-- you know, he wasn't officially like I was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I could go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we were going to pick up some people from an island, and some woman, which later on I did pick up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we seen, in a corner, the people was beating up, badly, a person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stopped the car, because we seen the person, you know, had no-- you know, a civilian, but had no star, nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know if he was Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we go down, two Germans get up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I, purposely, since I, you know, spoke Hungarian and everything, I told them, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you doing with this person?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, we recognize him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't wear a star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, I told him, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We take care of him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's give him to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, what are you going to do with him?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I tell him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I put the-- you know, I had the luger that-- you-- you know what we do with these people like this?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But not in the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I put him back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The poor kid was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, please don't kill me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Don't kill me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I told him, hey, listen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You don't have to worry about us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We're trying to save you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Tell me where would be the safest place for you, where we can let you go?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "First of all, I told him, clean yourself a little bit, because he looked bloody and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
